High Level Requirement
1.	Reducing paper and pen calculations – Just by entering the values you can perform the arithmetic operation to get the output.
2.	Performing specific calculation – Various operators will be available; the customer must pick the necessary one and he/she can continue with the calculations if needed.
3.	Clear – The customer can start from the first or exit the after performing any arithmetic operation.
4.	Availability of some special functions like area, square, factorial,etc.

